			though, it's really just this page.<br /><br />

			if you wanna get in touch for whatever reason, the best places to find me are on
			<a href="https://bsky.app/profile/gayfro.gs">bluesky</a> and <a href="https://discordapp.com/users/1103121656295198740">discord</a>.
			my handle is <emphasis>@gayfro.gs</emphasis> on both!

		</p>
	</main>
